      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CARRY ME PLEASE (8) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at this track following on from a third place finish (16.87) there the start prior. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from four starts. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. NANDO WATCH (7) produced a modest effort most recently when fifth at Q Lakeside over 352m behind Atomic Spider (20.67) in a Grade 6. Placed at his previous run. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Shapes as one to consider. QUARTER SHARE (1) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 300m (17.18). Comes through a solid form race last start. Should be about the mark. ZABDON MIRACLE (3) cannot be left out after placing last start.",
